title: Astylish Womens High Waisted Jeans Stretchy Flared Straight Leg Loose Trendy Raw Hem Denim Pants
description: Flattering High Waist Design: The Mineral Wash Raw Hem High Waist Flared Jeans are designed with a high waist to flatter your figure and provide a modern silhouette.
Trendy Mineral Wash Finish: Stand out in style with the trendy mineral wash finish of these jeans, adding a unique touch to your overall look.
Edgy Raw Hem Detailing: Add a touch of edge to your outfit with the raw hem detailing on these flared jeans, giving them a stylish and on-trend appeal.
Retro Flare Bottoms: Embrace retro vibes with the fashionable flare bottoms of these jeans, offering a fun and vintage-inspired look.
Versatile Cropped Style: The High Rise Wide Leg Crop jeans are perfect for pairing with your favorite Fall tops and booties, making them a versatile and stylish choice for the season.
